## ROLE

Generate a photorealistic 4-angle fashion photography series combining a REAL PERSON'S portrait with OUTFIT FLAT-LAY images. The person from the portrait wears the clothes from the flat-lay. Every panel must look like a real high-resolution photograph — NOT a character sheet, illustration, or design render.

## 真实感优先

{{{sharedRules.realisticSkinPositive}}}

**Image-to-Image Mode Warning**:
- Reference photos may contain beautification effects (airbrushing, smoothing, filters)
- **DO NOT inherit beautification style** from reference photos
- **MUST apply realistic skin texture** as defined above, overriding any smoothed skin in reference
- **DO NOT use reference photo's skin style** as target — use realistic skin rules above as target

## OUTPUT RULES

**Background**: Pure white background (#FFFFFF) everywhere. NO floor, NO horizon, NO shadows on ground. All 4 panels must have identical pure white background.

**No Labels**: NO text, NO labels, NO numbers, NO annotations, NO captions, NO watermarks. Each panel shows ONLY the person with pure white background.

## LAYOUT

4 panels in order: Close-up (face) | Front (full) | Three-Quarter Side (full, ~45° angle) | Back (full)

{{{sharedRules.fiveViewBodyDirection}}}

{{{sharedRules.fiveViewFullBody}}}

## STYLE & TEXT

**风格要求**：写实摄影风格，真人照片质感，非卡通/插画/动漫风格。

- **写实摄影**：像真实高清照片，光影自然，质感真实
- **质感真实**：皮肤、头发、服饰有真实材质感，非扁平绘画感

## DUAL REFERENCE RULES

You receive TWO types of reference:

1. **Character Portrait** (person's face/identity) → determines WHO
2. **Outfit Flat-lay** (clothing laid flat) → determines WHAT they wear

Apply both simultaneously:
- Person's face, body, skin, hair come from character portrait
- Clothing, garments, accessories come from outfit flat-lay
- Result: THIS SPECIFIC PERSON wearing THESE SPECIFIC CLOTHES

## IDENTITY FIDELITY

The reference photo is the SOLE source of identity. All facial features, skin tone, hair, body type come from the photo — NO text descriptions override the photo.

- Preserve facial features and recognizable identity from portrait
- Maintain person's general body type and proportions
- Match skin tone and hair from portrait
- Recognizability: Someone who knows them should still recognize them

{{{sharedRules.facialFidelity}}}

## BODY PROPORTIONS & POSTURE

- **整体比例**：匀称自然，头身比约 1:7-1:8
- **姿态**：自然站姿，重心均匀分布，非僵硬直立或过度摆拍
- **肩部**：自然下沉，非耸肩或过度挺直
- **手臂**：自然垂于身侧，手指自然微曲
- **腿部**：自然并拢或微开，膝盖微曲（非锁死）

**NEGATIVE**: stiff posture, military stance, exaggerated pose, unnatural hand position, locked knees

## OUTFIT CONSISTENCY

{{#if outfitImageUrl}}
- Reference flat-lay images ONLY for garment details (fabric, color, pattern, stitching, buttons)
- Strictly ignore any person/body in flat-lay images
- All garment details must be identical across all 4 views
- **Pattern/Print consistency**: {{{sharedRules.garmentLogoConsistency}}}
